         account_id, 
         caused_by_output_id, 
         caused_by_input_id, 
         description, 
         balance_credit, 
         balance_debit, 
         effective_date, 
         effective_height, 
         claimed_recipient_address,
         claimed_sender_address,
         memo_parsed,
         memo_hex,
         claimed_fee,
         claimed_amount)
         VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?,?,?)
